h3. Message Channel

Camel supports the [Message Channel|http://www.enterpriseintegrationpatterns.com/MessageChannel.html] from the [EIP patterns|Enterprise Integration Patterns]. The Message Channel is an internal implementation detail of the [Endpoint|http://camel.apache.org/maven/current/camel-core/apidocs/org/apache/camel/Endpoint.html] interface and all interactions with the Message Channel are via the Endpoint interfaces.

!http://www.enterpriseintegrationpatterns.com/img/MessageChannelSolution.gif!

For more details see

* [Message]
* [Message Endpoint]

